hi i'm paola

I was born and raised in San Francisco in the Excelsior district. I am a first-generation latina young woman learning how to navigate this thing we call life. I have a passion for learning and I enjoy trying new things and putting myself outside my comfort zone. I love to work with youth and the community to make a positive impact, I grew up in many non-profits that provided me with countless resources, and I love to pay that forward in any way I can.

Currently I am an Adventure Guide at the Tunnel Tops park, working with mostly youth and community groups to connect them with the outdoors. I also recently started to get on a path to studying Software Development. I am part of the Dev Mission Pre- Aprenticeship program and they have helped me grow my skills in HTML, CSS and JavaScript
